OL,3,CAscot Racecourse completes
OL,4,C'significant' solar panel project
OL,6,FAscot Racecourse has completed what
OL,7,Fit's called one of the largest on-site
OL,8,Fsolar installations in UK sport.
OL,10,FThe Berkshire racecourse has fitted
OL,11,Faround 1,200 solar panels across the
OL,12,Froof of its Grandstand.
OL,14,FIt says the panels will offset roughly
OL,15,F9% of its annual electricity
OL,16,Fconsumption and reduce its Carbon
OL,17,FDioxide (CO2) emissions by around 118
OL,18,Ftonnes in its first year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
