OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780920676
OL,3,CAscot Racecourse completes
OL,4,C'significant' solar panel project
OL,6,FThe system is planned to undergo final
OL,7,Fgrid connection and electrification
OL,8,Fthis summer, ahead of Royal Ascot.
OL,10,FThe completion of the works means
OL,11,FAscot now sits alongside the London
OL,12,FStadium and Manchester City's campus
OL,13,Fas leaders in the installation of such
OL,14,Fprojects, according to the racecourse.
OL,16,FAscot Racecourse Chief Executive
OL,17,FFelicity Barnard said the development
OL,18,Fmarks a "significant milestone".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
