PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780920676
OL,3,CAscot Racecourse completes
OL,4,C'significant' solar panel project
OL,6,F"It allows us to take a major step
OL,7,Fforward in our plans to cut emissions
OL,8,Fand strengthen the resilience of our
OL,9,Foperations," she said.
OL,11,F"By turning our Grandstand roof into a
OL,12,Flong-term energy asset, and bringing
OL,13,Fthe system online later this year, we
OL,14,Fwill be supporting both our
OL,15,Fenvironmental commitments and the
OL,16,Ffuture sustainability of the
OL,17,Fracecourse."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
